                <h1 align=left>Installing SHARPpy </h1> 
                <p align=left> To install SHARPpy on your computer:</p>
                <ol align=left>
                        <li>Download the SHARPPy package from GitHub by typing the following command in your command prompt:
                        <br>git clone http://github.com/sharppy
                        </li>
                        <li>Unzip the SHARPpy zip file.</li>
                        <li>cd into the directory and type in:<br>
                        python setup.py install
                        </li>
                        <li>Test the installation by loading up a Python terminal and typing:<br>
                        import sharppy</li>
                </ol>        
                        <h1 align=left>Documentation </h1> 
          <p align=left>Because this package is used by the scientific community, we ask that all contributors write well documented code and include references to peer-reviewed scientific journals in their code.</p>   				  
